OL,3,CMan charged after kidnap of teenage
OL,4,Cgirl in Altrincham
OL,6,FA man has been charged with a string
OL,7,Fof offences after a teenage girl was
OL,8,Fkidnapped in Altrincham.
OL,10,FPaul Sharpe, who's 56 and from
OL,11,FStockport, has been charged with:
OL,13,FHe's due to appear at Manchester
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,16,FThe 15-year-old girl, it is
OL,17,Funderstood, was forced into a vehicle
OL,18,Fon Bradgate Road, Bowdon, at around
OL,19,F6.45pm on Monday as she walked alone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
