OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779484267
OL,3,CMan charged after kidnap of teenage
OL,4,Cgirl in Altrincham
OL,6,FThe victim was missing for several
OL,7,Fhours on Monday, 18 May, and was found
OL,8,Fin the early hours of Tuesday, 19 May,
OL,9,Finside a vehicle in a hotel car park
OL,10,Fin Knutsford, Cheshire.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Justin
OL,13,FBryant, of the Criminal Investigation
OL,14,FDepartment in Trafford, said:
OL,15,F"Officers are continuing to work
OL,16,Ftirelessly on this investigation to
OL,17,Festablish the full circumstances
OL,18,Fsurrounding the incident.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
