OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779484267
OL,3,CMan charged after kidnap of teenage
OL,4,Cgirl in Altrincham
OL,6,F"The girl and her parents are now
OL,7,Fbeing supported by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers, who are working with her to
OL,9,Fbuild up a full picture of the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,F"As this is a live investigation,
OL,13,Fpeople should refrain from online
OL,14,Fspeculation.
OL,16,F"We would like to reassure the public
OL,17,Fthat there is no wider risk to the
OL,18,Fcommunity in connection with this
OL,19,Fmatter."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@HO]
